OL,3,CVictims sidelined in new 'outrageous'
OL,4,CBill, says Barnaby Webber's mother
OL,6,FThe mother of Nottingham attack victim
OL,7,FBarnaby Webber has branded new
OL,8,FGovernment legislation "utterly
OL,9,Foutrageous".
OL,11,FEmma Webber said the Victims and
OL,12,FCourts Bill - now moving through
OL,13,FParliament - would be "a betrayal" if
OL,14,Fpassed in its current form, and urged
OL,15,Fministers to urgently revise the
OL,16,Fproposals.
