OL,3,CVictims sidelined in new 'outrageous'
OL,4,CBill, says Barnaby Webber's mother
OL,6,FDiscretion of the information will be
OL,7,Fleft to hospital managers and
OL,8,Fprobation services instead, with
OL,9,Fvictims having no legal right to be
OL,10,Finformed, carry out a consultation or
OL,11,Fappeal any decisions.
OL,13,FValdo Calocane, who had been diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith paranoid schizophrenia, killed 19-
OL,15,Fyear-old students Barnaby and Grace
OL,16,FO'Malley-Kumar and 65-year-old
OL,17,Fcaretaker Ian Coates before attempting
OL,18,Fto kill three other people, in a spate
OL,19,Fof attacks in the city in June 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
