OL,3,CVictims sidelined in new 'outrageous'
OL,4,CBill, says Barnaby Webber's mother
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to an indefinite
OL,7,Fhospital order in January last year
OL,8,Fafter admitting manslaughter by
OL,9,Fdiminished responsibility and
OL,10,Fattempted murder.
OL,12,FA judge-led public inquiry into the
OL,13,Fdecisions made prior to the attacks
OL,14,Fwas announced in February and is due
OL,15,Fto take place later this year.
OL,17,FEmma Webber said the Bill would be "a
OL,18,Fbetrayal of every victim who has
OL,19,Falready been failed by this system" if
OL,20,Fit was passed into law in its current
OL,21,Fform.
