OL,3,CVictims sidelined in new 'outrageous'
OL,4,CBill, says Barnaby Webber's mother
OL,6,F"This must not happen. It is utterly
OL,7,Foutrageous that the Government would
OL,8,Feven contemplate this," she said.
OL,10,F"So egregious are the failings by
OL,11,Fevery single agency involved in every
OL,12,Faspect of our tragedy that a statutory
OL,13,Fpublic inquiry is under way.
OL,15,F"A significant part of the inquiry
OL,16,Fwill focus on the failings of
OL,17,F'hospital managers' and 'clinicians'
OL,18,Fwho failed to do their jobs properly.
OL,19,FResulting in the monster who killed my
OL,20,Fbeautiful child be allowed to roam the
OL,21,Fstreets and hide in plain sight."
