OL,3,CVictims sidelined in new 'outrageous'
OL,4,CBill, says Barnaby Webber's mother
OL,6,FMs Webber continued: "Why has the
OL,7,FGovernment chosen to include us as
OL,8,Ffamilies in the proposals for the
OL,9,Fmental health bill, revision of our
OL,10,Fhomicide laws and even the 10-year
OL,11,Fplan but conveniently chosen to ignore
OL,12,Fus on what is probably the one that
OL,13,Fwill affect us the most?"
OL,15,FIn a further letter written to two
OL,16,Fministers on Sunday, Ms Webber
OL,17,Frequested an urgent meeting to discuss
OL,18,Fher concerns and proposed amendments
OL,19,Fto the Bill.
