OL,6,FJulian Hendy, founder of Hundred
OL,7,FFamilies, said the Bill as it stands
OL,8,Fwas "not just a loophole, it's a kick
OL,9,Fin the teeth" for bereaved families
OL,10,Fand victims.
OL,12,FHe said: "We are talking about
OL,13,Foffenders who have been convicted of
OL,14,Fthe most serious of crimes, which
OL,15,Fcause extreme concern amongst the
OL,16,Fpublic.
